  "detailed_description": "<h1>FULL BODY TRACKING WITHOUT LIMITS</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/4cf6622d9361ef68661ce4823a413565.avif?t=1733815292\" width=616 height=346 /></span>No Full Body Tracking? NO PROBLEM! Play Dance Dash on PC with any webcam or phone, an AI powered camera-based full body tracking solution from Rebuff Reality.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/f5627d35be4a2245a9e3ea7647e366cf.avif?t=1733815292\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Step into the World of Dance Dash</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stomp the beats in this pulse-pounding, full body sensory symphony on your PC with webcam or VR Headset! Craft your own rhythm, groove to community maps, music, and mods. FREE DEMO.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your Gateway to Full Body Tracking</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/48b31ccddb68a91f268d0cbdf0b10d75.poster.avif?t=1733815292\" width=616 height=359 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/48b31ccddb68a91f268d0cbdf0b10d75.webm?t=1733815292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>FREE full body tracking with any mobile device, in-game YouTube dance videos and music videos to learn cool moves from the Pros.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/42eabd90babf88524faafa5596fab2d0.poster.avif?t=1733815292\" width=616 height=359 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/42eabd90babf88524faafa5596fab2d0.webm?t=1733815292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUST A MOVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dance Dash features intuitive mechanics like ducking, dodging, jumping, hitting, and especially shuffling, making it easy to play and highly engaging. Choreograph your most treasured tunes, and let the world know how you rock!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/6ba18782ab29e991bef5e0be809d4ebb.poster.avif?t=1733815292\" width=616 height=359 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/6ba18782ab29e991bef5e0be809d4ebb.webm?t=1733815292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY ANYTIME, ANYWHERE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dance Dash is designed to be user-friendly and easily playable on both PC and big screen TVs, providing a seamless and immersive experience. With simple setup and intuitive controls, players can enjoy full-body VR gaming in the comfort of their living rooms or home offices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/c24ff619d00f43d6e99e24bf39754bcc.poster.avif?t=1733815292\" width=616 height=359 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/c24ff619d00f43d6e99e24bf39754bcc.webm?t=1733815292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DD Editor to Create, Share, and Connect</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the DD Editor, to upload and view videos in-game, explore new tags and categories, and experience enhanced performance. Full mod capability is coming in June, offering endless customization options. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore, Dance, and Grow</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dance Dash isn’t just a game; it’s a community. Join our vibrant community of over 2,000 members and 10,000+ players from countries all over the world: ! Enjoy in-game YouTube dance and music videos, connect with fellow dancers. With Engine empower cross-platform play, the dance floor is always open.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to move, create, and connect in Dance Dash. Your dance journey starts now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Twitter: </u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Instagram:</u></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>TikToK: </u></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Official website:</u></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Contact Support:</u></i> <a href=\"mailto:dancedash@rebuffreality.com\">dancedash@rebuffreality.com</a></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/f5627d35be4a2245a9e3ea7647e366cf.avif?t=1733815292\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Step into the World of Dance Dash</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stomp the beats in this pulse-pounding, full body sensory symphony on your PC with webcam or VR Headset! Craft your own rhythm, groove to community maps, music, and mods. FREE DEMO.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your Gateway to Full Body Tracking</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/48b31ccddb68a91f268d0cbdf0b10d75.poster.avif?t=1733815292\" width=616 height=359 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/48b31ccddb68a91f268d0cbdf0b10d75.webm?t=1733815292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>FREE full body tracking with any mobile device, in-game YouTube dance videos and music videos to learn cool moves from the Pros.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/42eabd90babf88524faafa5596fab2d0.poster.avif?t=1733815292\" width=616 height=359 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/42eabd90babf88524faafa5596fab2d0.webm?t=1733815292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUST A MOVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dance Dash features intuitive mechanics like ducking, dodging, jumping, hitting, and especially shuffling, making it easy to play and highly engaging. Choreograph your most treasured tunes, and let the world know how you rock!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/6ba18782ab29e991bef5e0be809d4ebb.poster.avif?t=1733815292\" width=616 height=359 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/6ba18782ab29e991bef5e0be809d4ebb.webm?t=1733815292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY ANYTIME, ANYWHERE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dance Dash is designed to be user-friendly and easily playable on both PC and big screen TVs, providing a seamless and immersive experience. With simple setup and intuitive controls, players can enjoy full-body VR gaming in the comfort of their living rooms or home offices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/c24ff619d00f43d6e99e24bf39754bcc.poster.avif?t=1733815292\" width=616 height=359 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2005050/extras/c24ff619d00f43d6e99e24bf39754bcc.webm?t=1733815292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DD Editor to Create, Share, and Connect</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the DD Editor, to upload and view videos in-game, explore new tags and categories, and experience enhanced performance. Full mod capability is coming in June, offering endless customization options. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore, Dance, and Grow</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dance Dash isn’t just a game; it’s a community. Join our vibrant community of over 2,000 members and 10,000+ players from countries all over the world: ! Enjoy in-game YouTube dance and music videos, connect with fellow dancers. With Engine empower cross-platform play, the dance floor is always open.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to move, create, and connect in Dance Dash. Your dance journey starts now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Twitter: </u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Instagram:</u></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>TikToK: </u></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Official website:</u></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Contact Support:</u></i> <a href=\"mailto:dancedash@rebuffreality.com\">dancedash@rebuffreality.com</a></p>",
